name: MarvinInu
description: MarvinInu is a new ETH Crypto Token brought to you by fans in the community of Elon Musk’s gorgeous companion, Marvin. The #DogeFather himself is well known for his love of dog’s and we felt it’s time for Floki to move over and make way for Marvin to enjoy some of the spotlight. Based on the success of the token we will be working with dog shelters to assist them with the resources they need to help make all dogs feel loved and admired, just like Marvin! The team also has several plans in the works to create Marvin based NFT’s that collectors and fans around the world can purchase to show their love of Marvin and the Havanese breed.
